          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1628679846962-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1628679846962-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1628679846962-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the <strong>grated carrot</strong> and <strong>shredded lettuce</strong> – this is your <strong>salad</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>Korean yang-nyum fried cauliflower</strong> with the <strong>cooked sushi rice</strong> and <strong>salad</strong> to the side</p><p>Garnish the cauliflower with the <strong>sliced spring onion</strong> and drizzle the <strong>creamy Korean-style dressing</strong> over the salad</p><p>Enjoy</p>",
      "order": 8,
